{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_MAR_090.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, do you have a moment?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes, what is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Well, umm, I came here to explain something to you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Umm, explain what...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "You've been taking care of Linca a lot, right? But she's not good at talking..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "So I was worried about what kind of impression Linca gave you about me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh, like that story about making 100 friends? Or..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "That one! I was wondering if you thought I was someone who would give out absurd orders..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Umm...yes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xe9,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I knew it... Well, it definitely wasn't like that when I talked to her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0xed,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's just that Linca seriously latched onto an idea that I gave her as an example."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so that's what it was...<CR>Making 100 friends is preposterous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Linca was at her wit's end."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "She's bad at acting according to her circumstances. She's just so focused on carrying out her orders perfectly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I would like her to be able to take better care of herself, but it's not that easy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "When I gave her a list of ingredients to buy for dinner..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "She went all the way to Hornheim to gather all the ingredients on the list."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "It took her two weeks. That was a frightful experience..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Two weeks...? That's fourteen dinners..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure she's causing trouble for you, as well, but please go easy on her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "What? I've never thought that Linca caused me any trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Really? That's good... You're one of the few friends Linca has."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, Marion, you really do care about her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Hm? I guess. I'm responsible for looking after her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Plus, I want her to be happy. It's fine now, because I'm with her, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I can't guarantee that I'll always be there to look after her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "You're right. You might quit your job one day to become a mother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Of course, there's that too,<CR>but more so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I mean, I'm so busy, I don't have any time. And, I don't have anyone in mind in the first place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "But...I guess there might still be some hope for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "*ahem* Anyway, I just wanted to tell you that I hope you'll keep being Linca's friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "That's all. I'm kinda busy, so I'll get going now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "(She's so busy, but she came here for Linca's sake... She really does care about her a lot.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "(I'm not sure what I can do, but I'll be friends with Linca from now on, too!)"
        }
    ]
}